Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_min_capacitance(25.10)                      reset_min_capacitance(25.10)

Name
       reset_min_capacitance - Resets minimum capacitance limit specified (us-
       ing the the set_min_capacitance command) on objects in the object list

Syntax
       reset_min_capacitance

       <object_list>

       Resets  minimum  capacitance limit specified (using the the set_min_ca-
       pacitance command) on objects in the object list. The valid objects  in
       the object list are primary ports, clocks, and the current design.

Parameters
       <object_list>
              Specifies the list of ports, modules, and/or clock waveforms for
              which assertions are reset.

Related Information
       set_min_capacitance

